08140nam a22012615i 9783764384722DE-B159720211129102213.0m|||||o||d||||||||cr || ||||||||211129t20122007sz     fo  d z      eng d  a97837643847227 a10.1007/978-3-7643-8472-22doi  a(DE-B1597)206196  a(OCoLC)979884369  aDE-B1597bengcDE-B1597erda0 aeng  aszcCH 7aDES0000002bisacsh04a745.4072  aLH 795002rvk0(DE-625)rvk/95119:00aDesign Research Now :bEssays and Selected Projects /ced. by Ralf Michel. 1aBasel : bBirkhäuser, c[2012] 4c©2007  a1 online resource (254 p.)  atextbtxt2rdacontent  acomputerbc2rdamedia  aonline resourcebcr2rdacarrier  atext filebPDF2rda0 aBoard of International Research in Design00tFrontmatter -- tIntroduction -- tEssays I -- tThe Uneasy Relationship between Design and Design Research -- tFrom a Design Science to a Design Discipline: Understanding Designerly Ways of Knowing and Thinking -- tStrategies of Design Research: Productive Science and Rhetorical Inquiry -- tDesign Research, an Oxymoron? -- tDoing Design as a Part of Doing Research -- tResearch -- tShape of Things to Come -- tFor Inspiration Only -- tResearch through Design: a Camera Case Study -- tEmerging User Demands for Sustainable Solutions, EMUDE -- tEssays II -- tDesign Research and its Meaning to the Methodological Development of the Discipline -- tDesign as Practice, Science and Research -- tDesign Semiotics – Institutional Experiences and an Initiative for a Semiotic Theory of Form -- tDesign Research for Sustainable Social Innovation -- tBackmatter0 arestricted accessuhttp://purl.org/coar/access_right/c_16ecfonline access with authorization2star  aDesign entwickelt sich zu einer anerkannten wissenschaftlichen Disziplin und die Designforschung ist der treibende Bodensatz dieser Transformation. Design Research Now – Essays and Selected Projects vermisst das Feld der Designforschung anhand grundlegender Essays und ausgewählter Forschungsprojekte. Die Autoren der Essays, allesamt international führende Designwissenschaftler, nehmen zu den wichtigsten Fragen der Designforschung Stellung. Sie verorten die Bedeutung der Designforschung an der Schnittstelle zur Technologieentwicklung, beschreiben ihre Notwendigkeit für die methodische Weiterentwicklung der Entwurfsdisziplinen und ordnen ihr für die relevanten Entwicklungen der Gesellschaft eine bedeutende Rolle zu. Ergänzt werden die Essays durch die Darstellung aktueller, abgeschlossener Forschungsprojekte aus Hochschulen in den Niederlanden, Großbritannien und Italien.  aDesign is becoming a recognised academic discipline, and design research is the driving force behind this transformation. Design Research Now – Essays and Selected Projects charts the field of design research with introductory essays and selected research projects. The authors of the essays, all leading international design scholars, stake out positions on the most important issues of design research. They locate the significance of design research at the interface with technological development, describe what makes it a necessary ingredient of the continued development of the design disciplines, and assign it a seminal role in the relevant developments of society. The essays are supplemented by the presentation of recently completed research projects from universities in the Netherlands, the UK and Italy.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 0aArchitecture / Design. 0aDesign and construction. 4aBIRD. 4aDesign Research. 4aDesignforschung. 4aSwiss Design Network. 7aDESIGN / General.2bisacsh1 aBonsiepe, Gui, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBonsiepe, Gui.1 aBuchanan, Richard, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBuchanan, Richard.1 aChamberlain, Paul, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 